  </div>


    <section id="moduledoc">
<p>Native records processing functions.</p><p>This module contains functions for creating and inspecting native records.</p><section role="note" class="admonition warning"><h4 class="admonition-title warning">Warning</h4><p>The main purpose of the functions in this module is for debugging,
implementing library functions (such as printing of native records),
and implementing tools (such as the Debugger). Use with care in
applications.</p></section>
    </section>

</div>

