        <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
      </a>
      <span class="text">Summary</span>
    </h2>
<div class="summary-types summary">
  <h3>
    <a href="#types">Types</a>
  </h3>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#t:create_options/0" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">create_options()</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Options that can be used when creating a native record.</p></div>

    </div>

</div>
<div class="summary-functions summary">
  <h3>
    <a href="#functions">Functions</a>
  </h3>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#create/4" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">create(Module, RecordName, Fields, Options)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Takes <code class="inline">Fields</code> and creates a native record <code class="inline">Record</code> with module
<code class="inline">Module</code> and name <code class="inline">RecordName</code>.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#get/2" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">get(Key, Record)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Returns value <code class="inline">Value</code> associated with <code class="inline">Key</code> if native record <code class="inline">Record</code>
contains <code class="inline">Key</code>.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#get_definition/2" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">get_definition(Module, RecordName)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Retrieves the definition for native record <code class="inline">Name</code> in module <code class="inline">Module</code>.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#get_field_names/1" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">get_field_names(Record)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Returns a complete list of field names (keys) in native record <code class="inline">Record</code>, in
the order of declaration.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#get_module/1" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">get_module(Record)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Returns the module <code class="inline">Module</code> in which the native record <code class="inline">Record</code> is defined.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#get_name/1" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">get_name(Record)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Returns the name <code class="inline">Name</code> of the native record <code class="inline">Record</code>.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#is_exported/1" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">is_exported(Record)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Returns <code class="inline">true</code> if native record <code class="inline">Record</code> is exported; otherwise, returns
<code class="inline">false</code>.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#update/4" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">update(Src, Module, RecordName, FieldsMap)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Takes a map <code class="inline">FieldsMap</code> and updates the values in native record <code class="inline">Src</code>
as defined in module <code class="inline">Module</code> with name <code class="inline">RecordName</code>.</p></div>

    </div>

</div>

