          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



        <div class="specs">

            <pre translate="no"><span class="attribute">-type</span> create_options() :: #{is_exported := <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:boolean/0">boolean</a>()}.</pre>

        </div>


<p>Options that can be used when creating a native record.</p><ul><li>The value for the <code class="inline">is_exported</code> key should be a boolean indicating
whether this record value is exported.</li></ul><p>Consumed by:</p><ul><li><a href="#create/4"><code class="inline">records:create/4</code></a></li></ul>
  </section>
</section>

    </div>
  </section>

