          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Name = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:atom/0">atom</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>Returns the name <code class="inline">Name</code> of the native record <code class="inline">Record</code>.</p><p>This call fails with a <code class="inline">badarg</code> exception if <code class="inline">Record</code> is not a native record.</p><h2 id="get_name/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#get_name/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">R</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">records</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">create</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-1">(</span><span class="ss">test</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-2">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-3">{</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-3">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-2">]</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-4">#{</span><span class="ss">is_exported</span><span class="p">=&gt;</span><span class="ss">false</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-4">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">#</span><span class="nc">test</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-5">{</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-5">}</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">records</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">get_name</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-6">(</span><span class="n">R</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-6">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">records</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">get_name</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-7">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-8">#{</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-8">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5552782198-7">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gt">** exception error: bad argument
     in function  records:get_name/1
        called as records:get_name(#{})</span></code></pre>
  </section>
